name: Commission a Painting
description:
Have an idea for a cool painting? 

I readily accept commissions for interesting ideas which I can render in oils. Unique individual paintings vary in price depending upon size and complexity, generally exquisitley framed.

For guidelines only ........ 

10x8" £100-£150
16x20" £200-£250
28" plus £350+

Please contact me for a more precise estimate based upon your requirements. DO NOT CLICK BUY! I will bill you when the piece is completed.

name: Pet Portraits
description:
From your own photograph I will produce a pencil portrait to capture your best buddy for your wall. Dogs, cats, horses, pet goats! You will need to provide me with great photos from which to work.

Each piece is as unique as the character of the animal.

The finished pieces are mounted and framed at around 12x16".
